ence redefines storytelling by merging advanced spatial computing technology with emotionally resonant narratives.\n\n\"Out There\" showcases the exceptional voice talent of Grammy and Emmy-nominated artist Vanessa Williams, and is produced in collaboration with Pollen Music Group. Leveraging spatial audio and an innovative mix of 3D and traditional Disney-style 2D animation, this musical envelops you in a captivating, multi-dimensional world.\n\nEmbark on a magical journey that transcends traditional entertainment, and discover the future of immersive experiences with \"Out There.\" Available now on Meta Quest 3.", "short_description": "\"Out There\" - A Pioneering Immersive Musical Experience on Meta Quest 3\n\nEmbark on a magical journey that transcends traditional entertainment, and discover the future of immersive experiences with \"Out There.\" Available now on Meta Quest 3."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://fr.wilkins-avenue.com/out-there-privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Wilkins Avenue AR", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.wilkins-avenue.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "434961926215971"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["HAND_TRACKING", "OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8147786528646969"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "495792250049077"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "495792250049077"},